724
00:48:34.416 --> 00:48:36.292
Spiral of alerts. Mr. Secretary.

725
00:48:36.375 --> 00:48:38.542
And. uh. Dick's out of pocket right now.

726
00:48:38.625 --> 00:48:41.500
<i>But... when we increase our readiness...</i>

727
00:48:41.583 --> 00:48:43.333
-Sir.
-Yeah.

728
