729
00:48:44.916 --> 00:48:49.167
believing we're preparing to take
offensive action ourselves.

730
00:48:49.250 --> 00:48:51.958
Okay. what we need to do.
we need to communicate with them.

731
00:48:52.041 --> 00:48:55.333
-We need to... we need to explain our...
