740
00:49:17.000 --> 00:49:18.500
<i>I'm told imminent.</i>

741
00:49:18.583 --> 00:49:22.875
<i>It occurs to me.
do we have COG responsibility here?</i>

742
00:49:23.583 --> 00:49:26.000
I'll be taking your questions
at the later briefing this morning.

743
00:49:26.083 --> 00:49:28.208
so if you can just hold them until then.

744
00:49:30.166 --> 00:49:31.167
Sorry.

745
00:49:31.250 --> 00:49:33.541
<i>Sorry. Excuse me.</i>

746
00:49:34.916 --> 00:49:36.541
We still waiting on POTUS?

747
00:49:38.458 --> 00:49:39.500
What do you think?

748
00:49:40.541 --> 00:49:41.750
I'd be guessing.

749
00:49:41.833 --> 00:49:43.250
Where the hell is POTUS?

750
00:49:43.333 --> 00:49:44.625
North Koreans.

751
00:49:45.916 --> 00:49:47.333
Fuel shortages. Crop failures.

752
00:49:47.416 --> 00:49:49.500
Maybe they're more desperate
than we thought.

753
00:49:50.666 --> 00:49:51.625
B-2s are sortieing.

754
00:49:51.708 --> 00:49:54.916
Or it's Moscow. and they want us to think
it's the North Koreans.

755
00:49:56.666 --> 00:49:58.583
Moscow knows we'll retaliate.

756
00:49:58.666 --> 00:49:59.750
Do they?

757
00:50:00.916 --> 00:50:02.708
Assassinating dissidents
wherever they please.

758
00:50:02.791 --> 00:50:05.250
Imprisoning Americans. Ukraine.

759
00:50:05.750 --> 00:50:08.875
And what? We confiscate
a few of their yachts in Saint-Tropez?

760
00:50:10.125 --> 00:50:12.500
A single. unattributed strike

761
00:50:13.000 --> 00:50:14.083
sows chaos.

762
00:50:14.583 --> 00:50:16.000
puts us on our heels.

763
00:50:16.500 --> 00:50:19.667
and it gives them an opportunity
to see if they can get away with worse.

764
00:50:19.750 --> 00:50:21.791
Gives everyone that opportunity.

765
00:50:23.750 --> 00:50:27.750
Or some fucking sub captain woke up.
found out his wife left him. and snapped.

766
00:50:27.833 --> 00:50:29.750
-Yeah.
-Told you I'm guessing.

767
00:50:30.250 --> 00:50:31.250
Sir.

768
00:50:32.000 --> 00:50:33.000
Battle gram.

769
00:50:34.333 --> 00:50:36.000
Updating our target package.

770
00:50:37.250 --> 00:50:39.542
We're still trying
to ascertain that for you. sir.

771
00:50:39.625 --> 00:50:42.208
Greely better not fuck this up.

772
00:50:45.000 --> 00:50:46.833
I have an updated impact estimate.

773
00:50:47.333 --> 00:50:48.375
{\an8}<i>Go ahead. Tony.</i>

774
00:51:08.750 --> 00:51:11.875
-Hey. when are we home again?
-1700 next Tuesday.

775
00:51:11.958 --> 00:51:14.833
You think I can meet this girl
at the Applebee's before they close?

776
00:51:14.916 --> 00:51:18.500
-You take your dates to Applebee's?
-She works there. dumb-ass.

777
00:51:39.541 --> 00:51:41.541
<i>Jesus Christ.</i>

778
00:51:42.416 --> 00:51:46.042
{\an8}<i>This is why we have the GBIs.
No need to panic people.</i>

779
00:51:46.125 --> 00:51:47.750
