780
00:51:47.833 --> 00:51:50.666
Uh. yes. In the medium bucket.

781
00:51:51.916 --> 00:51:53.875
<i>My daughter lives in Chicago.</i>

782
00:51:55.250 --> 00:51:59.625
<i>Sir. our GBIs
will be airborne momentarily.</i>

783
00:51:59.708 --> 00:52:01.083
<i>This is what we do.</i>

784
00:52:02.500 --> 00:52:03.583
{\an8}<i>Jake. you still there?</i>

785
00:52:03.666 --> 00:52:04.750
Yes. sir.

786
00:52:05.333 --> 00:52:08.500
<i>What are the chances this works?
Knocking it down.</i>

787
00:52:09.083 --> 00:52:11.250
-General Brady should answer.
<i>-I'm asking you.</i>

788
00:52:11.333 --> 00:52:13.792
<i>-Yes. but...
-I know what he's gonna say.</i>

789
00:52:13.875 --> 00:52:15.416
<i>And I want the truth.</i>

790
00:52:18.208 --> 00:52:20.583
I should stay in my lane. sir.

791
00:52:21.083 --> 00:52:23.833
but... honestly...

792
00:52:23.916 --> 00:52:27.625
Interceptors have launched.
Everyone. interceptors have launched.

793
00:52:28.333 --> 00:52:31.125
<i>...it depends on the circumstances.</i>

794
00:52:31.875 --> 00:52:34.583
<i>Okay. when we... when we test...</i>

795
00:52:37.500 --> 00:52:39.042
When we test. we can't control...

796
00:52:39.125 --> 00:52:40.625
{\an8}<i>Cut the bullshit. damn it!</i>

797
00:52:43.833 --> 00:52:45.667
Once the kill vehicle separates.

798
00:52:45.750 --> 00:52:49.250
our mid course intercept system
has a success rate of 61%.

799
00:52:53.833 --> 00:52:55.416
<i>So it's a fucking coin toss?</i>

800
00:52:56.250 --> 00:52:58.708
<i>That's what $50 billion buys us?</i>

801
00:52:58.791 --> 00:53:01.291
We are talking about
hitting a bullet with a bullet.

802
