{\an8}<i>Hello? Hello? Can anyone hear me?</i>

803
00:53:04.333 --> 00:53:07.041
{\an8}<i>Mr. President. let's get you up to speed.</i>

804
00:53:07.916 --> 00:53:11.708
<i>Attention on the flight line.
Attention on the flight line.</i>

805
00:53:11.791 --> 00:53:13.792
<i>Ground crew to hangar three.</i>

806
00:53:13.875 --> 00:53:15.875
<i>Prep Ghost 1 for launch.</i>

807
00:53:17.958 --> 00:53:20.083
-This your office?
-Yeah.

808
00:53:20.166 --> 00:53:21.750
I need you to come with me. sir.

809
00:53:32.583 --> 00:53:34.750
<i>Fuel gauges checked!</i>

810
00:53:35.250 --> 00:53:37.833
<i>Flight controls.</i>

811
00:53:42.750 --> 00:53:43.958
<i>Munitions loaded.</i>

812
00:53:53.416 --> 00:53:55.708
Down the hall. Sir. we gotta move.

813
00:53:56.583 --> 00:53:59.250
-Sir. is everything okay?
-Gotta get to the elevator.

814
00:53:59.333 --> 00:54:02.208
-Marty. where are you going?
-Sir. we gotta get going now.

815
00:54:02.875 --> 00:54:03.875
Let's go.

816
00:54:41.958 --> 00:54:44.292
<i>-Could be a mistake.
-On our end or theirs?</i>

817
00:54:44.375 --> 00:54:45.375
<i>Who are they?</i>

818
00:54:45.458 --> 00:54:48.041
-Deputy NSA arriving.
-This way. sir.

819
00:54:49.208 --> 00:54:50.125
<i>Hold on.</i>

820
00:54:50.208 --> 00:54:54.708
<i>What I'm asking is. what are the odds
this is an intentional strike?</i>

821
00:54:54.791 --> 00:54:57.541
