938
01:01:08.291 --> 01:01:12.958
Jesus Christ. I got action in Khorramabad.
Sirens in Tel Aviv. sir.

939
01:01:13.041 --> 01:01:14.958
Everybody knows we missed.

940
01:01:16.666 --> 01:01:19.500
Mr. President. we're seeing
some concerning activity

941
01:01:19.583 --> 01:01:21.583
