946
01:01:36.333 --> 01:01:39.292
Until we know differently.
we have to assume this may get worse.

947
01:01:39.375 --> 01:01:43.000
{\an8}<i>General Brady. I know
everyone's trying to do their jobs here.</i>

948
01:01:43.541 --> 01:01:45.250
